" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Biclonal gammopathy",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 334px; height: 404px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Panel B: A biclonal pattern, with two small, discrete gamma bands, is seen on serum protein electrophoresis on agarose gel (anode on left). Panel A: Densitometer tracing of these findings shows the two protein peaks with gamma mobility.",
